    <measure>Pain intensity measured on a 10cm visual analog scale</measure>
    <time_frame>8 weeks after treatment</time_frame>
    <description>Patients will be asked to rate the pain intensity 8 weeks after treatment on a 10cm visual analog scale (0 indicating no pain, 10 indicating worst imaginable pain</description>
